## 4. Loudness Targets

All final deliverables must conform to modern web and broadcast standards to ensure a consistent and high-quality listening experience.

| Specification        | Target                                     |
| -------------------- | ------------------------------------------ |
| **Target Medium**    | Web / Online Content / Dialogue-centric Mix |
| **Integrated Loudness** | **-16 LUFS**                               |
| **True Peak Max**    | **-1.0 dBTP**                              |

*Note: The mix should feel dynamic and full without requiring aggressive compression. Ensure dialogue/VO remains clear and present at all times.*

